âš ï¸ Important Notes About Emojis

Emojis depend on font and terminal support

Some terminals may show emojis differently

Emojis work best in:

VS Code terminal

Windows Terminal

Modern Linux/macOS terminals

ğŸ“Œ ALT codes are Windows-specific
ğŸ“Œ Emojis are cross-platform Unicode characters

