ğŸ“š ALT Codes vs Emojis (Quick Comparison)

Feature	              ALT Codes	                    Emojis
Platform	           Windows only	               Cross-platform
Input	               Alt + Numpad	                  Unicode
Use case	           ASCII layouts	          UX & visual feedback
Style	                 Technical	            Friendly & expressive

